rows.label: tlk70000016_04_msg0001
rows.name:
You guys haven't just helped me.
You've helped all sorts of people, huh?

rows.label: tlk70000016_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Er, no, that's not it... I'm not frustrated
that you're helping other people
besides me. That'd be pretty selfish.

rows.label: tlk70000016_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't laugh, OK? There's a person
I really want to be there for right now,
and I can't stop thinking about them...

rows.label: tlk70000016_04_msg0005
rows.name:
You guys help tons of people, and I
only want to help one, but I can't...
That's what's frustrating me!

rows.label: tlk70000016_04_msg0006
rows.name:
But when I grow up I'm gonna be just
like you guys, you'll see! I'm gonna be
the best person I can.
